neo4jr_gen
=========

neo4jr_gen is a plugin that provides a generator for Neo4jr scaffolds.

The templates are based loosely on code from

http://github.com/andreasronge/neo4j-rails-example


Example
=======

From your rails root run:

    script/generate neo_scaffold Person name:string dob:date

Then add

    map.resources :people

to routes.rb

